Dialogs.Dialog: Hmm~... a sunburn it a bit...
Corn... fried noodles, ice cream... Fufu...
I must have a shrimp float...
Glass shoes... I think it's dangerous...
Mirror, mirror... The most delicious cake in the world... where is it...?
Candy house... it's all mine... Fufu.
I'm grateful for the heat... I'm 'kay...
I'll give you an injection... Fufu, it doesn't hurt, it doesn't hurt...
Fufu... Your pulse is high... What's wrong?
Welcome, kick... Ah... I made a mistake... Tehe.
Geez... I can't cook... anything sweet...
Rabbit goes Pyon Pyon... Pyon pyon pyon...
I'm looking forward to tomorrow's date...
I hope tomorrow comes soon... I'm kidding.
I wonder what kind of clothes would you like me to wear...
It's cute... I'm kidding, I was told that... Fufu!
Tomorrow... I'll be a lot more sweet than usual▼
If you're so nervous now... I wonder what will happen tomorrow...
I think it will be nice tomorrow... I want to see you tomorrow...
...Didn't you find anything strange about me yesterday?
I wonder if I was too playful yesterday... maybe I'm a little sleepy...
I wonder we should go next, I'm kidding. Fufu, I'm a quick one.
...You're so unfair. Why are you so nice?
At your house, it was just the two of us... right? ...It's embarrassing...
...I wonder why you are so excited. Ha~...
I wish I could be with you all the time...
I'm good at this kind of things... I'll listen to you next time▼
There are two weeks left... It's a little... unfair...
I wonder if I should call you... I want you to call me.
I can't concentrate with you around, but I'm making progress. Fufu, it's mysterious.
The fact you were studying seriously was wonderful...
I wish we made a promise today...
An alarm... Hmm, it's fine... I can ask Mama to do it...?
I wonder what kind of boyfriend I can meet tomorrow...
May tomorrow be a wonderful day. I'm kidding.
A kiss it's strange... I wonder why it can make me so happy...
I wonder if I'll be good if I was fluffier...?
More... I wonder if I'm not strange for asking for it...
...Ah~. I'm relieved... I'll kiss you like that...
I can't tell you it's not enough...
Just remembering what will happen next... I wonder what will happen...
I wonder why it's like this... I...
I like you... I love you. I love you so much...
My world is dyed with your colors... I'm kidding.
I want to see you in my dreams... I wonder if you will come to see me.
This is so engrossing, it's a foul! I'm kidding...
I wonder what should I do. I really can't sleep...
I didn't know I was so greedy... ha~h...
I want to hear your voice... I wonder if you will call me...
I wonder what are you doing now, you... you won't get anything...
Is it a luxury to be worried about someone else?
I wonder how I was spending time before I met you...
If I say I'm lonely, you might be worried. But, I want you to be a little...
A lot more... I want to be together...
I wonder what a boy thinks about...
I wonder if it was a mistake...
I don't want to feel like this... idiot...
My eyelids, are heavy... but I have to get up... but I'm sleepy...
A moderate rest is part of your studies, isn't it?
Good luck♪ take care of the next problem! ...I'm kidding.
That treatment might be good... I hope your hair becomes nice and smooth.
Ah~, no... in such a place... don't let him notice!
I wonder if it isn't fun to be home alone...
...This is it, isn't it? Maybe we can meet on the way...
...Hmm, I'll invite you. I'm sure it's delicious.
It's boring to have a meal alone...
I thought you said you wanted to take a break... ha~h...
I wonder what happened... No, I have to concentrate.
Say good night with me... I'm kidding, that's no good...
I was up. Well, if it's just a little, it's okay. Shall we talk?
If you don't sleep, tomorrow will be hard? I'm kidding. Hey, shall we say good night?
Good morning... Emm, aren't you sleepy? Is so, then don't!
Good morning. Shall we eat breakfast?... Let's eat. Fufu!
Good morning, have you wake up yet? Ready for breakfast? I'm kidding.
Ah. It's no good to wake up before me. I'm kidding. Good morning▼
It's already noon. I wonder what should I do. What do you want to eat? I'll prepare it♪
I have to eat well and prepare for afternoon. Right~?
Wouldn't it be nice if there was a school route where you can take a nap after lunch? I'm kidding.
Thank you for your hard work. Let's take a break together.
Today's dinner? I haven't thought about it yet. If you want anything just ask▼
...Are you tired? Yes, let's relax a little? I'll relax too.
I see, I had no homework. Hmm... I want to talk for a while...
Ah~, the bath water is already hot... Geez. Don't think weird things okay?
I'm going to sleep while reading a book in my futon. Hmm, I'll lend it to you next time, okay?
Huh, you are still up... are you okay? Isn't that prohibited?
Yes, I was sleeping... It's okay. I woke up, so we will be together, right?
Hey~, let's go to sleep at the same time, okay?... I feel lonely if you go...
I'm glad, I was really worried... I wondered if nothing happened. I'm really happy you came.
I'm so happy to have fun every day... Thank you for making me happy.
If you feel like this, you'll love it, right?
You don't really like this, do you....?
I hope you would tell me I'm cute...
That's a bold arrangement... I mean, what if I'm surprised?
I wonder how I can make a cute coordination...
Ah~. Isn't this good? Yes, isn't that right?
Hmm~, it's decided... But, it might have been nice...?
I know, let's send an e-mail...
That sentence... I wonder if it's okay...
I wonder if it should be written more cutely...
It's a mail from you after all.
I'm glad I received an e-mail...
! I was surprised... it's exciting even to receive an e-mail... I'm kidding, geez...
And sent. I hope you will notice it soon. I'm kidding.
I hope the reply will come soon...
I sent an e-mail... I'm kidding。
Emm, what I need tomorrow is...
It's certainly in the living room...
Fufu, it smells good. I'm healed...
Emm... no. What should I do. It's not broken, right?
I ate a lot of sweets... I have to be careful.
Ah, it's decreasing... I wonder why.
When I'm on a date, I eat a lot...?
I see. We've been eating out less...
Hmm, it's delicious. Self- praising. Fufufu!
No matter where you go, it's not embarrassing. I'm kidding。
I've prepared it well, so I want you to try it...
...Is it a little different from usual? Emm, maybe with more sugar?
Ah~. The order is different... Hmm, it's fine, I can do it.
...I wonder if it's okay. I feel different...
Phew~. Surprisingly, I need power... Hmm~!
I wonder if you will happy with my lunch...
The color... Yes, it's beautiful. The taste is also perfect. Fufu!
I hope you find it delicious.
Let's do out best with new dishes!
...Next, I'll let you know it'll be delicious.
I'll do my best next time▼
Wow, it's cute... I like it...
There are also ways to dress like that... Hmm...
It's good, but it doesn't suit me...
Ah~, it's wonderful. I have to check.
This kind of thing is popular now. I see...
In that case, I can make it. Let's see...
Ah~, this seems convenient... Let's see it next time.
Looks delicious... I'll try it next time.
With you house heat, cold won't do anything to you...
I wonder if this is good... I'll use as reference when making bentos▼
Phew. My tummy is full. It was delicious♪
A little more... just a little more...
Fu~, I woke up. Hmm, let's have breakfast.
It looks like someone is watching...
Hey~, why don't we talk a little?
Hey, is it okay? I want to talk.
▲主人公＊▲. Is it time to talk with me? I'm kidding.
I want to talk a little bit. Right?
Look over there?... Hey, shall we talk?
Did you have anything good today?
Um, I wonder if you have somewhere you want to go. Let's go there next time, okay?
If you have any worries, please tell me anytime okay?
Ah~!... Did you get stuck? Fufufu!
Hey, can you tell me something you've been up to lately?
Please tell me if you found an interesting program, okay? I'll negotiate with Papa♪
Hey, what kind of dream did you have recently? Was it fun?
Did you finish your homework?... Hmm, let's take a break today. Fufu!
I want to eat a cake with seasonal fruits...
Isn't the club practice a bit though? I'll do my best to keep up.
Do you know any interesting movie? I'm a little worried.
Emm... Yes, did you see it? Because... I won't tell you.
Why don't you look at Fortune-telling? I'm watching it in the news paper.
Hey, are you familiar with games? If you have one, I would like to try.
I wonder what kind of place would you like to go on a trip... I'll research it. Fufu!
Hmm~ Hmm, nothing. Shall we continue?
Are you okay with this time? I'm okay.
Hey... Can't you hear me? I see...
Are you busy? Well then, want to leave?
...What's wrong? Should I do it later?
Emm. I wonder what should I do.
If you want to talk, call me anytime, okay?
Hmm? It's already good... I'm kidding. See you.
That you for this good time. See you later, okay?
Hmm, let's talk again, okay? See you.
More... it's no good... See you.
It's a good prospect after all▼
Is that so... I can still go...
Hey~, are you doing well these days?
Fufu~, I guessed right. I'm in good shape, I'm kidding♪
Hey~, aren't you feeling sick at this point?
That was fine. I feel relived.
Is that so... I worry about sickeness, so cheer up okay?
Hey, have you been depressed recently? I feel like that...
...Do you want my energy? Anywhere, as much as you want. Okay?
I'm glad. If you think it's too much, take a rest, okay?
Hey, don't you think you're overdoing it today? I'm worried...
I've been jogging. It does feel good early in the morning, right?
This morning breakfast is salted salmon, miso soup, pickles, natto... Don't over eat okay?
Today I took a walk with Mama. Papa is away.
I wake up early, even on my days off... I wonder if that's a waste.
Sometimes I don't want to get out of the futon, which is not good.
The morning drama novel is really good. I'm get anxious every episode...
This morning, I had you wake me up in a dream. Thank you, I'm kidding.
I was surprised when time catched up and I was relax- ing, reading a newspaper. I have to be careful.
I was troubled because I couldn't do my uniform tie. This happens sometimes.
For breakfast? Did you eat fresh bread? It was fluffy and delicious▼
Today, I didn't do anything and tried to relax. But I couldn't so I cleaned my room. Fufu.
When I went shopping, I saw some nice clothes... Hey, want to go with me next time?
I played the piano leisurely ... I really like playing piano.
Today I'm making bread with Mama! I made some.
The lunchtime purchasing department is truly amazing ...I wonder what happens when a new thing comes out.
I exchanged lunch boxes with my friends and it was delicious. I was praised.
Seems that some construction started near. I'm worried so I can't concentrate, so I want to finish early...
In the hallway, when I accidentally yelled, my friend saw me... It was embarrassing...
When the weather is nice, you might want to get out and play... right? I'm kidding。
...I just ate snacks with my classmates. Is that good for anyone?
In the garden of the corner, the flowers I saw were blooming. I wonder if birds carry the seeds.
I got some freshly picked vegetables from my neighbors. I'm looking forward to cook them.
When I went to a cake shop, my favorite cake was sold out. Next time, I have to go earlier.
I wanted to play, so I took a walk with the dogs♪ I want to go again.
I'm hungry... Don't be tempted okay? I won't be washed away.
The atmosphere in the corridor in the evening is nice, isn't it? Isn't it a little scary at night?
The vending machine seems to be broken. It was supposed to be a dark machine... What is that?
The school gate was repainted, right? I have to be careful not to touch it.
During break time, I had my friends tell me about hair arrangements. I've learned a lot♪
I saw the sunset on the rooftop with my friends. It was so beautiful... I wanted to see it with you.
Today, I tried a little elaborated cooking... want to taste?
Papa made dinner for me today. Yes, it was delicious. Mama was smiling too.
Wait... I was surprised by my toughts when I lay on bed... What if you couldn't sleep...
I thought I should try to stay up late, but... I decided to stop.
I also made notes for the test, and I'm wondering if I can relax after that. How about you do it?
A doogy somewhere was howling in response to the police siren. Hey, it was cute.
I tried using a new bath salt and it was so pleasant because it smelled good. Try it next time, okay?
After stretching in the living room, Papa and Mama started to work together, right? Fufu, it was fun.
When I took a bath, I was surprised when the electri city suddenly went off. I wish it didn't...
Preparations, review, tomorrow is okay. I'm kidding. Fufu!
If you read a new work of your favorite writter... I may be sleepy.
I was chatting with Mama the other day. Mama was also playing.
Hmm... Yes. are going to sleep? You stay late at night too?
After a long nap, I can't sleep. Can I sleep after drinking hot milk?
I was thirsty and woke up, and when I went to the living room... Papa was working...
I was solving a difficult math problem... It's vexing to fall asleep without knowing the answer, right?
I drank some strong tea and my eyes became heavy... I wonder what should I do if I become sleepy duing class.
Since Papa and Mama were sleeping, I secretly watched TV... Is that the only one when you can shop online?
Just outside, a loud noise! It was so loud that I jumped. I hope it was not an accident...
What would happen to me if I woke up until late morning ... I want to try it.
Do you like to move your body?
Hey, are you good at drawing?
Hey, how do you do your cleaning?
Hey, aren't you trying to collect your laundry?
You like going out to play, do you?
Are you fond of chilling indoors?
Do you like to relax in the park?
You look around old buildings, are you interested?
Hey, do you like moving your body?
Hey, are you fond of eating?
Hey, are you interested in photography? Ah~, a shotting chance?
Hey, do you like the quiet atmosphere of the church?
Hey, where do you want to live?
Hey, do you like playing games?
Do you usually listen to music?
Are you fond of amusement park dates?
Hey, are you good at swimming?
Hey, do you like watching the stars?
Hey, do you like flowers and plants?
Hey, when there's an event, do you go see it?
Hey, do you like going to the sea?
...This is a girl's swimsuit ... are you interested?
Hey, do you want to climb a mountain?
Hey, are you fond of playing in the nature?
Hey, isn't it nice to take a bath?
Um, what do you do before going to bed?
Tell me, what is your favorite love movie?
Hey, do you have any favorite dishes from the ones I cooked?
Hey, are you sure you want to eat Western food as breakfast? Or Japanese food?
Do you want to listen to my piano performance?
Are there any countries or places you would like to visit together?
Um, where is your favorite place when going on a date?
Hey, do you want to fall in love like in fairy tales?
Hey, do you get excited when going on dates?
Hey, your first love... I wonder if it was me.
Hey, should I rub your shoulders?
Hey, what do you think about living with me...?
Hey, it's our anniversary. Did you remember it?
Emm. Isn't that... liked by girls? ...In many ways.
That's right. I heard something good.
After all? Yes, I feel like that.
Yes, somehow I wanted to ask.
I know one more thing about you. Fufu.
I wanted to know more about you...
That's what it feels like... Hmm...
Sorry, the same thing many times. I wonder what is happening.
That's right, I've heard it several times. But tell me, please?
Hey~ the bigger a boy is, the better... right?
Yes... but how big is it... Ah~, it's nothing!
It's normal, right? Yes. Is that wrong?
...I knew it... I wonder if I should do a diet...
Really? I'm glad... Thank you for listening.
I feel like I've been a little fluffy lately. Is that okay?
Really?... I wonder if the health meter is wrong.
I'm glad. I've been eating a lot lately, so I'm interested.
Is that so... I haven't gained weight. I wonder what should I do.
Hey, can you tell me about your favorite food?
What do you think about unclassified dishes?
I'm glad. Hmm? I'm looking forward ot it.
Is that so?... I have to practice. Yes.
Don't you want to give someone you like delicious food?
Hmm... practice, I don't have to skip it.
I got a new recipe this time. When I make it, can you try it?
I found another recipe that looks delicious. I'm looking forward to make it♪
I've been making Western food recently. I also thought about an original menu.
Recently I've been trying to make Chinese food. I should stick to the seasonings... Fufu, are you worried?
I've been making Japanese food recently. It's a lot of fun, because I don't know much yet.
I'm good at cooking regardless of the food when asked about food.
Recently, I've been wanting to make sweets again... I have to be careful not to get fat.
Hey, what should we do in this date... have you decided?
Is that so. Then, are you looking forward to it?
Well then, let's think together. I wonder where we should go.
Is it a place where you can move freely?
Maybe it would be good to go to a busy place?
Hmm... maybe you want to go to a place you've never been to.
Those places are the best for dates, right?
What was the most enjoyable place you went to?
A place with delicious shops nearby! I'm kidding.
Then, why don't we go somewhere indoors?
Yes, what about somewhere you can enjoy outside?
Hmm~... how about this? We can see events and exhibitions.
Hey~, are we going to shop on this date?
Hey~, what about somewhere we can move freely for our next date?
Hey~, we should have a date where we can relax, right?
Hey~, isn't it good that we can play on this date?
You will change it. Thank you.
Fufu, it's decided! I'm looking forward to it▼
We can go wherever you like?
Ah~, meanie. I'm kidding. Then, you can leave it to me, right?
Isn't it fun we thought the same thing?
Yes, I'm looking forward to it. I'm kidding.
Maybe it's good to go back to school?
Don't forget to check the delicious food shops. Right?
Let's have a nice date, okay?
I wonder what kind of clothes I should wear...
I want the day to come soon. Fufu!
I have to be careful to not delay my return back home. Right?
...Hey. You've been kissed by your girlfriend... did you like it?
Hmm? Then, we're free to do anything? I'm kidding.
That's right. It's embarrassing... Hmm. I get it.
That's right. Then, can I leave it to you? I'm kidding.
... Yes... Ah~, no. It's nothing. Don't worry, okay?
Do boys like to... forcefully kiss their partners?
That's right. Eh... I don't hate that, but... don't look at me so much.
Is that right?... Sometimes I think that's good? I'm kidding。
I'm happy you care about me. Thank you...
Hey, where do you like to do skinship?
I also feel relived, when you touch me.
...It's embarrassing. When I heard that I...
Fufu, my upper arms? I'm kidding.
I like it too. Your hands are warm.
... Yes. When you're hugged ... do you feel happy?
Hey, do you like to play or being played with?
I like it too. It's a bit embarrassing...
Really? I was also yearning for it.
If there are only two people, it should be dignified... I'm kidding.
Is that so? I am... a little bit.
...Yes. Hmm... isn't it embarrassing just us?
I'm not that bad, right? I'm sorry.
Hey, have you been sleeping properly lately?
Exercise? Are you doing it properly?
When you go to bed, do you turn off the cooler?
Hey, tell me please? As your girlfriend, I want to know.
Geez... don't forget I worry about you, okay?
Did you finish? I won't lose.
You did your best. As expected.
Is that so... I'm worried okay? Let's be careful.
Shall we do it a little more? Right?
Emm... really? Let's improve little by little. Right?
It's no good... can you do it better? Please.
Sleep properly, okay? Not at the same time as me, though. Right?
Shall we start with light exercises? I'll support you too!
Are you eating breakfast? Hey, can we eat together?
Isn't it good to have a snack? I'll be careful too.
Geez... don't catch a cold, okay? Try to sleep warmly.
Don't leave it on, absolutely don't. Turn on and sleep, right?... I have to remember that too.
Was it fun when we went out today?
Hey, wasn't it fun when we went out last time?
We played various games, right? Let's go play together again, okay?
I'm happy that the photo you took will be something to remember.
The medal game is exciting. I want to do it again.
The jackpot was amazing! I hope we can see it again.
I got a scratch card. Hey, can we try again?
What? It was sudden... I'm embarrassed.
Geez, I can't hear that... I won't tell you!
I can't hear you with my heart beating this way...
I don't want you to say that so lightly...
...I love you. I love you as the best in the world, okay?
I like you. Ah~, I'm sorry... I love you.
I won't go with someone I don't like. I'm kidding.
...Do you like me? But... I want you to think about me a little more.
Hmm. If it's just a little...
I don't know what you're thinking...
Geez. I will tell you that sort of thing.
Perhaps we are... an idiot couple?
You can only talk about this between couples, right?
Geez, I can't keep returning with a smile.
▲主人公＊▲... I wanted to call you.
Geez, meanie. I'll be listening too.
Hey, I want to hear it too, okay?
Hey. Let me know too, please?
▲新主人公▲. What would you think if you were called...?
Really? Well then, shall we call?
▲新主人公▲... I'm sorry, I'm still embarrassed. Can we do it again next time?
Is that so. Then, shall I stop? It was a bit fresh. Fufu!
You know? I have something to talk about... can you listen to me?
Come closer, please? I don't want people to ask me...
Hey, can you hear me? If you can, say "I hear you", okay?
I can't think of anything but you...
It's almost the end of the year. Let's do the countdown together... I'm kidding.
The year-end and New Year holidays were fun. This year will be wonderful.
Valentine's Day is coming soon. There's no need to do research.
Thank you for making me happy in Valentine's. I feel rewarded.
White Day is coming soon. Don't worry too much.
Thank you for the White Day's gift. Actually... I was expecting it.
April Fool's Day is coming soon. The sad lie is... me!
I just remembered April Fool's Days
There will be an excursion soon. I have to prepare for it.
It was a fun excursion. I want to do it each month.
There will be a chorus competition soon. I wonder if I'll do it well.
The chorus competition was a good memory... I did my best.
Tanabata is coming soon. I have to think about my wishes.
Tanabata was fun. I enjoyed the event.
The Tohano Festival is coming soon. I wonder what kind of excitement I will have this year...
The Tohano Festival was fun. It's a fun festival♪
It will be a sports festival soon. Let's start a special training! I'm kidding.
Sports festival was fun. It has a different sense of accomplishment than club activities.
Halloween is coming soon. Maybe I'll make a Jack-o- lantern.
Halloween was fun. It was a little embarrassing, though.
Cultural festival is coming soon. I want to make this year's school festival a wonderful memory.
The cultural was fun. It was good to work hard.
Christmas is coming soon... I definitely want to be with you...
Thank you for those Christmas memories. Aika is happy.
Your birthday is soon... What would you like?
Let's do our best. It it doesn't work, I'm sorry.
...I see. Emm, can you hold it?
Isn't your birthday near? Do you have something you want...?
Correct answer? Congratulations to you. Fufu.
The correct answer is...? A kiss from you. It's a little but more special than usual...
Well, the correct answer is... a special time to spend with you. I'm kidding.
Hey, how do you want to spend our anniversary?
Me? Am I happy just to be with you?
Hey? I wonder if you want something to commemorate.
Hmm... can you think about it?
Hey, what are your aspirations for this year?
Yes, you can do it. I'll support you!
My aspirations? They have to be... being with you? Fufu.
Is my aspiration to give our best together? ...It's a lot, isn't it?
This moth is already over... What is the most funny thing to do these days?
I want to see the cherry blossoms. The cherry blossoms are beautiful...
I have eaten strawberries. Strawberries are delicious▼
I played under the sun. I like the spring breeze and the sun.
I have a fan with me. Fufu, are you a child?
I ate a delicious shaved ice. The taste of ice is different, isn't it?
I lighted fireworks in the garden. I like sparklers the most...
I enjoyed the taste of autumn▼ I was able to cook a lot of food... I'm very satisfied. Fufu.
I've seen a lot of old movie DVD's. It's autumn of art. I'm kidding.
Am I enjoying autumn colors? It's bright and very beautiful.
I made various hot pots. Eating cabbage pots with ponzu sauce is recommended by the Tanake family▼
I snowed. I watched it inside my room.
I just ate ice cream. Of course, I also got mandarin orange▼
Hey, do you have time now? If you are free, can we play together?
Hey, are you busy? I want to play... I'm kidding.
If you have some free time, can you please help me? I'm kidding.
Hey, did you find it interesting? Will you do it again?
Then, let's do it again okay?
I'll tell you that sort of thing soon... Is that special?
Hey, were are we going to play?
Do you like me to spoil you?
Do you want Eal Kung Fu?
I won't lose next time, okay?
Not that? Then... at the next opportunity.
Well then, can we play "Just Count"? If you think 30 seconds passed, say "high", okay? I'll take the time.
Then, shall we start? Okay... start!
Ah~, it's too bad! It was just a little off.
Sorry... it was a bit late. You have to say "high", right?
You haven't been e-mailing me much, have you?
Thank you for always sending me e-mails... Thank you really. I'm happy.
I'm lonely lately because I can't go out with you... If you're not busy, can we date?
Thank you for always taking somewhere new... Thank you really. Can we do it again in the future?
You haven't been calling me lately, have you? I would be happy just to hear your voice.
Can you call me more, that way we can spend less time away, right?
Recently, I feel you've been distant... We don't have much skinship.
I suppose I wouldn't know that skinship was good if I didn't meet you...
Thank you for always listening to me... I don't hate skinship while talking...
...That's a lot of skin- shipping, so it's weird not to be touched. Isn't it your fault?
You know? A forced kiss... sometimes it's a little... but, yeah! It's good!
...Your aggresive way of kissing... I'm not sure. I'm kidding。
Kiss... I want you to kiss me more... how should I say it?
Kiss me then... I feel very happy. Thank you for making me happy.
The feeling of distance between us is melting... I like it.
I feel like we're the best couple. Don't you think so too?
Hey, have you recently met the person who introduced us?
I wonder if the person who introduced us is doing fine.
We had a double date... I had a good time. I wish I could do it again.
Did you understand some things from the double date? Let's try it again, okay?
The other day, I talked to a friend who has a boyfriend. It was a lot of fun♪
I had a girl-talk with my friend... The contents are secret▼
Why do you care about it? I'm not saying anything strange, so rest assured, okay?
...Maybe it's melted? As much as everyone.
Hey, I sent you an e-mail, did you read it? If you haven't, why not take a look?
Did you hear the message on the answering machine? Please check it when you have time.
The WEB magazine has been updated?
Hey, can you look over there? Hu-rry-up.
